'''Farmers''' are [[monster]]s who can be found walking around farm areas. Farmers require level 10 [[Thieving]] to be [[Thieving#Pickpocket|pickpocketed]], and if they are pickpocketed successfully, players will receive 9 [[coins]] and 14.5 Thieving [[experience]].

==Locations==

* North of [[East Ardougne]] (4)
* South of [[Falador]] (1)
* [[Lumbridge]] farms
* South of [[Varrock]]

